A Perfect Murder;;51;;57;;R;;Wall Street baron Steven Taylor (Michael Douglas) discovers that his pretty young wife, Emily (Gwyneth Paltrow), is cheating on him. But what concerns him more than her infidelity is the hope of profiting from her untimely death. Emily has millions, and Steve's own financial empire is collapsing before his eyes. He hires her lover, David (Viggo Mortensen), to murder her. The plan -- to stage a break-in that will look like a random murder -- turns out to be far from perfect.;;Mystery & thriller;;Andrew Davis;;1998;;Michael Douglas,Gwyneth Paltrow,Viggo Mortensen,David Suchet,Sarita Choudhury,Constance Towers,Michael P. Moran,Novella Nelson,Arnold Kopelson,Anne Kopelson,Christopher Mankiewicz,Peter Macgregor-Scott,Stephen Joel Brown;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1083171-perfect_murder